OL,3,CAcademies Trust to stop running
OL,4,Cseveral schools amid alleged budget
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FThe UBAT which currently runs 11
OL,8,Fprimary schools and three secondary
OL,9,Fschools in Sussex - including
OL,10,FHastings, Burgess Hill and St Leonards
OL,11,FAcademies, is believed to have kept
OL,12,Faround 20% of the funding.
OL,14,FStaff at five schools which the Trust
OL,15,Fruns went on strike earlier this year,
OL,16,Fwith picket lines held in Burgess Hill
OL,17,Fand Hastings.
OL,19,FBut now the Trust has announced it is
OL,20,Foffloading the schools to other
OL,21,Facademy trusts.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
