OL,7,FIn a letter to parents it says it is
OL,8,Ffacing 'times of challenge and times
OL,9,Fof change'.
OL,11,FThe MP for Hastings and Rye, Helena
OL,12,FDollimore said she welcomes the
OL,13,Fannouncement. Speaking to ITV
OL,14,FMeridian's Political Correspondent she
OL,15,Fsaid: "The current situation could not
OL,16,Fcontinue - we have too many children
OL,17,Fin Hastings and Rye being failed by
OL,18,Flocal schools and that needs to change.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
