OL,4,Cseveral schools amid alleged budget
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,F"This Trust has been taking a whopping
OL,8,F20% of the government grant meant for
OL,9,Four local schools, using it for back-
OL,10,Foffice costs like executive salaries."
OL,12,F"Last month, I raised this in the
OL,13,FHouse of Commons and the Minister
OL,14,Fconfirmed this could not continue, so
OL,15,FI welcome the news today. It's an
OL,16,Fopportunity for a fresh start for our
OL,17,Flocal schools so that we can make sure
OL,18,Fwe drive up standards and get every
OL,19,Fchild in Hastings and Rye the best
OL,20,Fquality education.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
