OL,3,CAcademies Trust to stop running
OL,4,Cseveral schools amid alleged budget
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,F"And now we have an opportunity to
OL,8,Freset that and drive up standards."
OL,10,FA UBAT spokesperson said: "The Board
OL,11,Fof Trustees of University of Brighton
OL,12,FAcademies Trust met on Friday 10
OL,13,FJanuary to consider the future of the
OL,14,FTrust.
OL,16,F"Following this meeting, the Trustees
OL,17,Fhave informed the Department for
OL,18,FEducation of their desire to seek to
OL,19,Ftransfer the academies in the Trust to
OL,20,Fother Academy Trusts.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
